title: Milo Yiannopoulos resigns from Breitbart News - Washington Times
text:
View Comments Print By Victor Morton - The Washington Times - Updated: 2:48 p.m. on Tuesday, February 21, 2017 
Gay provocateur Milo Yiannopoulos has resigned his position at Breitbart News, just days after an interview resurfaced in which he defended underage pederasty.
